  "privacy.s2.bizH": "Business data:",
  "privacy.s2.h": "2. What data we collect",
  "privacy.s2.p": "We collect the following categories of personal data:",
  "privacy.s2.usageH": "Usage data:",
  "privacy.s2.use1": "Login activity and session data",
  "privacy.s2.use2": "IP address and browser information",
  "privacy.s2.use3": "Platform usage statistics",
  "privacy.s2.use4": "Error logs and technical diagnostics",
  "privacy.s3.h": "3. How we use your data",
  "privacy.s3.li1": "Providing and maintaining our calendar booking service",
  "privacy.s3.li2": "Processing bookings and appointments",
  "privacy.s3.li3": "Sending confirmation and reminder emails",
  "privacy.s3.li4": "Providing customer service and technical support",
  "privacy.s3.li5": "Improving our service and user experience",
  "privacy.s3.li6": "Complying with legal obligations",
  "privacy.s3.li7": "Preventing fraud and abuse",
  "privacy.s3.p": "We use your personal data for the following purposes:",
  "privacy.s4.h": "4. Data sharing and disclosure",
  "privacy.s4.l1": "With your consent:",
  "privacy.s4.l2": "Service providers:",
  "privacy.s4.l3": "Legal requirements:",
  "privacy.s4.l4": "Business transfer:",
  "privacy.s4.p": "We do not share your personal data with third parties, except in the following cases:",
  "privacy.s4.v1": "When you have explicitly consented to sharing",
  "privacy.s4.v2": "Trusted partners who help us deliver the service (hosting, email, payment)",
  "privacy.s4.v3": "When required by law or court orders",
  "privacy.s4.v4": "In case of merger, acquisition or sale of business parts",
  "privacy.s5.h": "5. Data security",
  "privacy.s5.org1": "Limited access to data",
  "privacy.s5.org2": "Regular security audits",
  "privacy.s5.org3": "Employee training",
  "privacy.s5.org4": "Incident response procedures",
  "privacy.s5.orgH": "Organizational security:",
  "privacy.s5.p": "We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data:",
  "privacy.s5.tech1": "SSL/TLS encryption",
  "privacy.s5.tech2": "Secure databases",
  "privacy.s5.tech3": "Regular security updates",
  "privacy.s5.tech4": "Access controls",
  "privacy.s5.techH": "Technical security:",
  "privacy.s6.h": "6. Your rights under GDPR",
  "privacy.s6.p": "As an EU resident, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:",
  "privacy.s6.r1h": "Right of access",
  "privacy.s6.r1p": "You can request a copy of all personal data we have about you",
  "privacy.s6.r2h": "Right to rectification",
  "privacy.s6.r2p": "You can request correction of incorrect or incomplete data",
  "privacy.s6.r3h": "Right to erasure",
  "privacy.s6.r3p": "You can request deletion of your personal data",
  "privacy.s6.r4h": "Right to data portability",
  "privacy.s6.r4p": "You can request your data in a machine-readable format",
  "privacy.s7.h": "7. Data retention",
  "privacy.s7.l1": "Active accounts:",
  "privacy.s7.l2": "Closed accounts:",
  "privacy.s7.l3": "Booking data:",
  "privacy.s7.l4": "Log files:",
  "privacy.s7.p": "We only retain your data as long as necessary for the purposes for which it was collected:",
  "privacy.s7.v1": "As long as your account is active",
  "privacy.s7.v2": "Up to 30 days after closure (unless legally required otherwise)",
  "privacy.s7.v3": "Up to 7 years for administrative purposes",
  "privacy.s7.v4": "Maximum 12 months",
  "privacy.s8.closing": "You can manage cookies through your browser settings, but this may affect functionality.",
  "privacy.s8.h": "8. Cookies and tracking",
  "privacy.s8.li1": "Remembering your preferences and login status",
  "privacy.s8.li2": "Analyzing website usage for improvements",
  "privacy.s8.li3": "Providing personalized user experience",
  "privacy.s8.p": "Our website uses cookies and similar technologies for:",
  "privacy.s9.h": "9. Changes to this privacy policy",
  "privacy.s9.p": "We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of important changes via email or a prominent notice on our website. The date of the last change is always displayed at the top of this document.",
  "privacy.title": "Privacy Policy",
