  "whyus.cardBack.c1Content": "Your assistant answers on WhatsApp around the clock, so customers can book, reschedule or cancel at any hour, even when you are closed. Every request is captured instead of lost to a missed call or a full voicemail.",
  "whyus.cardBack.c1Title": "Always taking bookings",
  "whyus.cardBack.c2Content": "Customers book in the WhatsApp they already use every day, so there is nothing to download and no account to create. That lower threshold means more requests actually turn into booked appointments.",
  "whyus.cardBack.c2Title": "No app to install",
  "whyus.cardBack.c3Content": "While traditional booking methods take minutes or hours, our AI responds instantly to customer inquiries. This includes understanding context, checking availability, and confirming appointments - all in under 30 seconds on average.",
  "whyus.cardBack.c3Title": "30sec Average Response",
  "whyus.cardBack.c4Content": "Automatic WhatsApp reminders and one-tap rescheduling make it easy for customers to keep or move an appointment instead of just not turning up. Because people actually read WhatsApp, the reminders land where email often doesn't.",
  "whyus.cardBack.c4Title": "Reminders that cut no-shows",
  "whyus.caseDisclaimer.tag1": "6-12 month performance tracking",
  "whyus.caseDisclaimer.tag2": "Results vary by implementation",
  "whyus.caseDisclaimer.text": "Based on verified business performance data from in-depth case studies",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1After": "WhatsApp automation handles bookings instantly 24/7. Staff focus on patient care instead of answering phones. Zero double bookings with real-time calendar sync.",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Before": "Receptionists spent 3+ hours daily playing phone tag - patients calling during busy hours, getting voicemail, calling back repeatedly. Manual appointment book checking during calls caused 2-3 minute holds. Double bookings happened weekly.",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Impl1": "24/7 WhatsApp booking bot with calendar integration",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Impl2": "Automated reminders 24h + 2h before appointments",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Impl3": "Instant confirmations with appointment details",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Impl4": "Easy rescheduling without calling office",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1MobileAfter": "24/7 instant booking, zero phone tag, no scheduling conflicts.",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1MobileBefore": "3hrs daily phone tag, manual scheduling, double bookings weekly.",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Quote": "Our staff used to spend half their day answering the same booking questions. Now they can focus on what matters - taking care of patients.",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Res1": "3 hours/day staff time saved on phone calls",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Res2": "50% reduction in no-shows with WhatsApp reminders",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Res3": "35% more bookings from after-hours availability",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s1Res4": "Zero double bookings with automated calendar sync",
