  "whyus.caseStudies.s3After": "WhatsApp bot handles complex scheduling instantly, syncing with attorney calendars and court dates. Clients book preferred times without phone tag.",
  "whyus.caseStudies.s3Before": "Consultation scheduling took 4-6 phone calls per client - attorney availability checks, court schedule conflicts, client callback loops. Receptionists spent 40% of their time on booking coordination.",
