  "whyus.methodology.caseLimitations": "Case studies represent individual business results. Outcomes may vary based on business size, implementation quality, staff training, and industry-specific factors. Results reflect businesses that completed full integration and training programs.",
  "whyus.methodology.caseOverview": "Our case studies methodology involves comprehensive business performance analysis before and after WhatsApp integration. Each case study represents verified business results tracked through multiple measurement systems and validated by third-party audits over 6-12 month periods.",
